          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We make a little Futurelife breakfast and mill around, enjoying having nothing to do. Jordan has a sleep and I fiddle around with Bovineiterology. Gilson approaches me with a question of if we’d like to go sailing - yes please! We arrange to take the big catamaran out to the island that afternoon for a sunset sail. ",
            "link": null
